OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782413298
OL,3,CYvette Cooper backs Burnham for Labour
OL,4,Cleadership
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper has
OL,7,Fthrown her support behind Andy Burnham
OL,8,Fto take the keys to Number 10, after
OL,9,FSir Keir Starmer's decision to step
OL,10,Faway from the Labour leadership and
OL,11,Fhis role as prime minister.
OL,13,FSpeaking to ITV News Political Editor
OL,14,FRobert Peston, Cooper said Burnham is
OL,15,F"the right person" to lead the party
OL,16,Fafter Labour's dismal performance in
OL,17,Flocal and national elections.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782413298
OL,3,CYvette Cooper backs Burnham for Labour
OL,4,Cleadership
OL,6,F"It's really important that we can all
OL,7,Fget behind Andy Burnham as the next
OL,8,FPrime Minister, and to make sure that
OL,9,Fwe can reach out to people who have
OL,10,Flost confidence in us and earn back
OL,11,Fthat support and respect," she said.
OL,13,FAnd, with Burnham's coronation seeming
OL,14,Fmore and more likely, Cooper declined
OL,15,Fto go into private conversations she
OL,16,Fhas had with the newly minted
OL,17,FMakerfield MP - but did disclose that
OL,18,Fthe pair had been in contact over
OL,19,FUkraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782413298
OL,3,CYvette Cooper backs Burnham for Labour
OL,4,Cleadership
OL,6,FCooper, who was speaking to ITV News
OL,7,Ffrom the Ukraine Recovery Conference
OL,8,Fin Poland, said that Burnham, like
OL,9,FStarmer, is "100% behind our
OL,10,Funwavering support for Ukraine, its
OL,11,Fdefence, its security and its future".
OL,13,FThe foreign secretary acknowledged
OL,14,Fthat local election results have been
OL,15,Fa wake-up call for the party, and that
OL,16,Fministers needed to recognise that
OL,17,Fvoters no longer believed Labour was
OL,18,Fon their side.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782413298
OL,3,CYvette Cooper backs Burnham for Labour
OL,4,Cleadership
OL,6,F"We had to face the results and also
OL,7,Fto recognise that they were really bad
OL,8,Fresults for us," she said. "We had to
OL,9,Flisten to what people were saying
OL,10,Facross the country."
OL,12,FWhile refusing to discuss private
OL,13,Fconversations surrounding Starmer's
OL,14,Fdeparture, Cooper praised the outgoing
OL,15,Fprime minister's record, saying Labour
OL,16,Fwould never have returned to
OL,17,Fgovernment without his leadership.
OL,19,F"It's only as a result of his
OL,20,Fleadership that Labour got into
OL,21,Fgovernment," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782413298
OL,3,CYvette Cooper backs Burnham for Labour
OL,4,Cleadership
OL,6,FAnd, as the party looks to reset
OL,7,Fitself, rebuild trust with voters and
OL,8,Fprevent a political vacuum filled by
OL,9,F"hardliners and extremists" - the
OL,10,Fforeign secretary pointed to Burnham's
OL,11,Fsuccess in Makerfield.
OL,13,F"Andy's shown it's possible to turn
OL,14,Fthat around and reach into communities
OL,15,Frooted in Labour values. That is
OL,16,Freally important, and that's why I
OL,17,Fthink he is the right person to be the
OL,18,Fnext prime minister."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
