CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782413298
OL,3,CYvette Cooper backs Burnham for Labour
OL,4,Cleadership
OL,6,FAsked whether she wanted to remain
OL,7,Fforeign secretary in a future Burnham
OL,8,Fgovernment, Cooper said any decisions
OL,9,Fon Cabinet appointments would be a
OL,10,Fmatter for the incoming leader.
OL,12,FShe also declined to be drawn on
OL,13,Freports Burnham could bring former
OL,14,Fsenior civil servant Olly Robbins back
OL,15,Finto government.
OL,17,FCooper also confirmed that all British
OL,18,Fembassy staff in Venezuela had been
OL,19,Faccounted for following a devastating
OL,20,Fearthquake in the country
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782413298
OL,3,CYvette Cooper backs Burnham for Labour
OL,4,Cleadership
OL,6,FThe UK has announced #2 million in
OL,7,Femergency humanitarian assistance and
OL,8,Fis working with international partners
OL,9,Fto support relief efforts.
OL,11,F"All of the embassy staff and those
OL,12,Fconnected to them have been accounted
OL,13,Ffor and are safe," Cooper said.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
