OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782413298
OL,3,CYvette Cooper backs Burnham for Labour
OL,4,Cleadership
OL,6,FAsked why Labour has never elected a
OL,7,Fwoman as permanent leader and prime
OL,8,Fminister, Cooper acknowledged the
OL,9,Fparty still had work to do
OL,11,F"Of course I want to see a woman
OL,12,Fleader in the future," she said.
OL,14,FBut she insisted her focus was now on
OL,15,Fsupporting Burnham and helping Labour
OL,16,Fregain the confidence of voters.
OL,18,F"We've got to earn back respect and
OL,19,Fsupport," she said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
